Extrasensory perception and distant-viewing

Distant-viewing is ability to see or feel something which other senses cannot
feel. Is it really real or it is just conspirator theory?

Existence of so-called ESP is based on some individual cases which happened in
random moment and often were not repeated again. Those cases which was repeated,
were more likely magician performance, quote favorite of mine tells “Do not
believe anything you hear and only half what you see”. There is not a single
repeatable scientist experiment, that measured anything enough successful so we
can trust it and prove that ESP exists.

On the other hand, I ret interesting article about army mission where group of
soldiers were about to came into trap, but minutes before one of them stopped
them and told them that he had bad feel about that path. Somebody can express
that as distant-viewing because he did not see anything suspicious, he heard
nothing and had no chance to know that it was a trap. From my perspective, I
see it as just long experience from his subconscious, which sometimes cannot be
explained because its complexity.

In conclusion I do not think that ESP is real.